lParagraphs:
	-
		lSentences:
		-
			en: A long time ago, there was a naughty child named Aladdin.
			zh: 很久以前, 有个淘气的孩子, 名叫阿拉丁.
			pinyin: Hěnjiǔ yǐqián, yǒu gè táoqì de háizi, míng jiào ā lādīng.
		-
			en: His father died when he was ten years old, and they were dependent on each other.
			zh: 他十岁的时候父亲就去世了, 和母亲相依为命.
			pinyin: Tā shí suì de shíhòu fùqīn jiù qùshìle, hé mǔqīn xiāngyīwéimìng.
			lPhrases:
				-
					en: died
					zh: 去世了
					pinyin: qùshìle
				-
					en: dependent on each other
					zh: 相依为命
					pinyin: xiāngyīwéimìng
	-
		lSentences:
		-
			en: One day, a magician came to the village.
			zh: 有一天, 一位魔法师来到村庄.
			pinyin: Yǒu yītiān, yī wèi mófǎshī lái dào cūnzhuāng.
		-
			en: He said he was Aladdin's uncle, and he wanted to take Aladdin to do business.
			zh: 他说他是阿拉丁的叔叔, 要带阿拉丁去做生意.
			pinyin: Tā shuō tā shì ā lādīng de shūshu, yào dài ā lādīng qù zuò shēngyì.
	-
		lSentences:
		-
			en: The magician took Aladdin into the mountains and chanted a spell.
			zh: 魔法师吧阿拉丁带到进山, 念起了咒语.
			pinyin: Mófǎ shī bǎ ā lādīng dài dào jìn shān, niàn qǐle zhòuyǔ.
		-
			en: With a "bang", the ground shook.
			zh: "砰" 的一声, 地面摇了一下.
			pinyin: "Pēng" de yīshēng, dìmiàn yáole yīxià.
		-
			en: Then they saw a square/adj rock appear on the ground.
			zh: 然后他们看到地上出现了一块正方形的石头。
			pinyin: Ránhòu tāmen kàn dào dìshàng chūxiànle yīkuài zhèngfāngxíng de shítou.
	-
		lSentences:
		-
			en: The magician put a special ring on Aladdin's finger.
			zh: 魔法师把一枚特别的戒指套在阿拉丁的手指上.
			pinyin: Mófǎ shī bǎ yī méi tèbié de jièzhǐ tào zài ā lādīng de shǒuzhǐ shàng.
		-
			en: He said "You take out the oil lamp out of the cave."
			zh: 他说：“你把油灯从山洞里拿出来。”
			pinyin: Tā shuō:“Nǐ bǎ yóudēng cóng shāndòng lǐ ná chūlái.”
		-
			en: "We can share the gems in the cave."
			zh: “我们可以分享洞穴里的宝石。”
			pinyin: “Wǒmen kěyǐ fēnxiǎng dòngxué lǐ de bǎoshí.”
	-
		lSentences:
		-
			en: Aladdin found the oil lamp, but he didn't want to give it to the magician.
			zh: 阿拉丁找到了那盏油灯, 但他不想给魔法师.
			pinyin: Ā lādīng zhǎodàole nà zhǎn yóudēng, dàn tā bùxiǎng gěi mófǎ shī.
		-
			en: In a rage, the magician closed the door of the cave.
			zh: 魔法师一怒之下, 关上了洞门.
			pinyin: Mófǎ shī yī nù zhī xià, guānshàngle dòng mén.
	-
		lSentences:
		-
			en: Aladdin was scared.
			zh: 阿拉丁很害怕.
			pinyin: Ā lādīng hěn hàipà.
		-
			en: He accidentally rubbed his hand on the magic ring.
			zh: 他的手无意中在魔戒上擦了一下.
			pinyin: Tā de shǒu wúyì zhōng zài mó jiè shàng cāle yīxià.
			lPhrases:
				-
					en: magic ring
					zh: 魔戒
					pinyin: mó jiè
		-
			en: A strange man flew in front of Aladdin.
			zh: 一个奇怪的男人飞到阿拉丁面前.
			pinyin: Yīgè qíguài de nánrén fēi dào ā lādīng miànqián.
			lPhrases:
				-
					en: in front of
					zh: 面前
					pinyin: miàn qián
		-
			en: He was a Genie.
			zh: 他是一个精灵.
			pinyin: Tā shì yīgè jīnglíng.
		-
			en: Aladdin asked the Genie to take him home.
			zh: 阿拉丁请求戒指精灵送他回家.
			pinyin: Ā lādīng qǐngqiú jièzhǐ jīnglíng sòng tā huí jiā.
	-
		lSentences:
		-
			en: The Genie took Aladdin home.
			zh: 戒指精灵把阿拉丁送回了家.
			pinyin: Jièzhǐ jīnglíng bǎ ā lādīng sòng huíle jiā.
		-
			en: Aladdin wanted to exchange the oil lamp for something to eat.
			zh: 阿拉丁想用油灯换点吃的。
			pinyin: Ā lādīng xiǎng yòng yóudēng huàn diǎn chī de.
		-
			en: So, he wiped the dust off the lamp.
			zh: 所以，他擦掉了灯上的灰尘。
			pinyin: Suǒyǐ, tā cā diàole dēng shàng de huīchén.
		-
			en: Suddenly, another genie flew in front of him.
			zh: 突然, 另一个精灵飞到他面前.
			pinyin: Túrán, lìng yīgè jīnglíng fēi dào tā miànqián.
	-
		lSentences:
		-
			en: With the help of the magic lamp, Aladdin and his mother lived a long and prosperous life.
			zh: 有了神灯的帮助, 阿拉丁和母过着长和富足的生活.
			pinyin: Yǒule shén dēng de bāngzhù, ā lādīng hé mǔqīn guòzhe zhǎng hé fùzú de shēnghuó.
			lPhrases:
				-
					en: magic lamp
					zh: 神灯
					pinyin: shén dēng
	-
		lSentences:
		-
			en: When the king's parade passed by, Aladdin fell in love with the beautiful princess at first sight.
			zh: 在国王的御驾经过的时候, 阿拉丁对美丽的公主一见钟情.
			pinyin: Zài guówáng de yùjià jīngguò de shíhòu, ā lādīng duì měilì de gōngzhǔ yījiàn zhōngqíng.
			lPhrases:
				-
					en: fell in love
					zh: 钟情
					pinyin: zhōngqíng
				-
					en: at first sight
					zh: 一见
					pinyin: yījiàn
		-
			en: Aladdin asked the Genie to build him a beautiful palace.
			zh: 阿拉丁请求精灵为他建造一座美丽的宫殿。
			pinyin: Ā lādīng qǐngqiú jīnglíng wèi tā jiànzào yīzuò měilì de gōngdiàn.
		-
			en: The king agreed to the marriage.
			zh: 国王同意了这桩婚事。
			pinyin: Guówáng tóngyìle zhè zhuāng hūnshì.
	-
		lSentences:
		-
			en: The magician disguised himself as a seller of oil lamps.
			zh: 魔法师化装成卖油灯的小贩.
			pinyin: Mófǎ shī huàzhuāng chéng mài yóudēng de xiǎofàn.
		-
			en: He came to Aladdin's palace.
			zh: 他来到阿拉丁的宫殿前.
			pinyin: Tā lái dào ā lādīng de gōngdiàn qián.
		-
			en: He stole the magic lamp while Aladdin was not at home.
			zh: 他趁阿拉丁不在家, 骗走了神灯.
			pinyin: Tā chèn ā lādīng bù zàijiā, piàn zǒule shén dēng.
	-
		lSentences:
		-
			en: The magician forced the Genie change Aladdin's palace and princess.
			zh: 魔术师强迫精灵改变阿拉丁的宫殿和公主。
			pinyin: Móshù shī qiǎngpò jīnglíng gǎibiàn ā lādīng de gōngdiàn hé gōngzhǔ.
		-
			en: The king was very angry when he saw it.
			zh: 国王见了非常生气.
			pinyin: Guówáng jiànle fēicháng shēngqì.
	-
		lSentences:
		-
			en: The Ring Genie told Aladdin what happened and took him to the palace.
			zh: 戒指精灵告诉阿拉丁发生了什么事，并把他带到了宫殿。
			pinyin: Jiè zhǐ jīnglíng gàosù ā lādīng fāshēngle shénme shì, bìng bǎ tā dài dàole gōngdiàn.
		-
			en: Aladdin found the princess and gave her some special powder.
			zh: 阿拉丁找到了公主, 给了她一些特别的粉末.
			pinyin: Ā lādīng zhǎodàole gōngzhǔ, gěile tā yīxiē tèbié de fěnmò.
	-
		lSentences:
		-
			en: That night, the magician returned.
			zh: 当天晚上, 魔法师回来了.
			pinyin: Dàngtiān wǎnshàng, mófǎ shī huíláile.
		-
			en: The princess pretended to invite him to drink wine with enthusiasm.
			zh: 公主假装热情地请他喝酒.
			pinyin: Gōngzhǔ jiǎzhuāng rèqíng de qǐng tā hējiǔ.
		-
			en: The magician drank the wine with powder added and passed out.
			zh: 魔法师喝了加了粉末的就, 昏了过去.
			pinyin: Mófǎ shī hēle jiāle fěnmò de jiù, hūnle guòqù.
	-
		lSentences:
		-
			en: Aladdin took back the magic lamp and asked the Genie to take them back home.
			zh: 阿拉丁拿回神灯, 让灯神带他们回到了家.
			pinyin: Ā lādīng ná huí shén dēng, ràng dēng shén dài tāmen huí dàole jiā.
		-
			en: Since then, they have lived a happy life.
			zh: 从那以后, 他们过着幸福美满的生活.
			pinyin: Cóng nà yǐhòu, tāmenguòzhe xìngfú měimǎn de shēnghuó.
